      <h2>What is meditation?</h2>
      <p>
        Meditiation is a mind training technique to develop mental quality. It is something we can incorporate
        into our daily life, allowing us to improve the quality of the mind and the body. Meditation is not only
        for monks or priests but is a practice for anyone who would like to improve their quality of life.
      </p>
