      <h2>What is Dhammakaya meditation?</h2>
      <p>
        Dhammakaya meditation is one of several meditation techniques which has been practiced in Asia for over
        two thousand and five hundred years. It is effective and easy to learn. Everyone, regardless of age, race
        or beliefs, can obtain the benefits from this technique.
      </p>
